## 4️ Creating a Test Share

`[notes] comment = CheckIT path = /mnt/notes/ browseable = yes read only = no writable = yes guest ok = yes enable privileges = yes create mask = 0777 directory mask = 0777`

Restart Samba to apply changes:

`sudo systemctl restart smbd`

