## 5️ SMB Enumeration with smbclient

`# List server shares (anonymous) smbclient -N -L //10.129.14.128  # Connect to specific share smbclient //10.129.14.128/notes  # Commands in smbclient ls           # list files get <file>   # download file put <file>   # upload file !ls          # run local command help         # all smbclient commands`

