## 8️ RPCclient (Manual SMB Enumeration)

`rpcclient -U "" 10.129.14.128   # anonymous  # Commands srvinfo                  # server info enumdomains              # list domains querydominfo             # domain details netshareenumall          # list shares netsharegetinfo <share>  # share info enumdomusers             # list users queryuser <RID>          # user info querygroup <RID>         # group info`

**Brute-force RIDs example:**

`for i in $(seq 500 1100); do   rpcclient -N -U "" 10.129.14.128 -c "queryuser 0x$(printf '%x\n' $i)" \   | grep "User Name\|user_rid\|group_rid" && echo "" done`

